race.comment: ZEAL BEAUTY (6) made a big impression on debut when flew the lids from the middle with a strong turn of foot, going on to clock 20.46 when a 3.5 lengths winner over 365m at this track. Can measure up again if runs up to debut effort. MYSTERIOUSLY (8) ran good time (20.69) when second last start over 365m at this track, the second placing in a row. Well placed here and can atone this time. ROMANI LASS (2) placed last time at big odds - worth some thought. Something for the Multiples: LOCK STAR (5)
